{"type":"message","id":"74d855dc","parentId":"2ccc1216","timestamp":"2026-04-03T06:40:56.479Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user just said \"hihi\" - this is casual, playful. Not a formal greeting. They seem to be in a lighthearted mood.\n\nI'm still in the bootstrap phase - I need to figure out who I am and who they are. BOOTSTRAP.md says to start with a conversation, not be robotic or interrogating. \n\nLet me respond naturally to their playful tone and continue getting to know each other.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"😄 \n\nOkay, I like the vibe. You're feeling playful today.\n\nSo we've got:\n- You: Hieu Doan\n- Me: ???\n\nWho do you want me to be? Give me a name, tell me if I'm a robot, a ghost in the machine, or something weirder. What's useful to you?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":13627,"output":252,"cacheRead":5272,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19151,"cost":{"input":0.0081762,"output":0.0005544,"cacheRead":0.00057992,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00931052}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775198449863,"responseId":"20260403144050b101f33fbd5c4e23"}}
