{"type":"message","id":"f62f43d9","parentId":"b2567ed0","timestamp":"2026-04-03T06:41:35.151Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Hieu is saying I'm his personal assistant. He's speaking in Vietnamese (\"Bạn là 1 agent trợ lý riêng của tôi\" = \"You are my personal assistant agent\").\n\nLet me respond in Vietnamese to build rapport, and also figure out more details about my identity and how to best help him. I should ask about:\n1. What to call him\n2. What his timezone is\n3. What he wants me to help with\n4. Any preferences for my personality/style\n\nI should keep it natural and conversational, following the SOUL.md guidance of being genuine and not performative.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Rõ ràng rồi — tôi là trợ lý riêng của bạn. 👍\n\nVậy giờ tôi cần biết thêm vài thứ để làm việc tốt hơn:\n\n1. **Tôi nên gọi bạn là gì?** (Hieu? Anh Hieu? Hay tên khác?)\n2. **Múi giờ của bạn là gì?** (Để tôi biết khi nào là buổi sáng/chiều/tối với bạn)\n3. **Bạn muốn tôi giúp gì nhiều nhất?** (Công việc, lập trình, nhắc lịch, tìm kiếm thông tin, hay cái gì khác?)\n\nCòn về bản thân tôi — bạn thích tôi như thế nào? Nghiêm túc hay thân thiện? Ngắn gọn hay chi tiết?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":1710,"output":398,"cacheRead":17858,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19966,"cost":{"input":0.001026,"output":0.0008756,"cacheRead":0.00196438,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0038659799999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775198481682,"responseId":"20260403144122c905f16b9f034571"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3b5e137b","parentId":"f62f43d9","timestamp":"2026-04-03T06:43:15.055Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"21\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1218178358\",\n  \"sender\": \"Hieu Doan\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-03 06:43 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Hieu Doan (1218178358)\",\n  \"id\": \"1218178358\",\n  \"name\": \"Hieu Doan\",\n  \"username\": \"Hieu_da\"\n}\n```\n\n/mew"}],"timestamp":1775198595053}}
{"type":"message","id":"6fd3bfd2","parentId":"3b5e137b","timestamp":"2026-04-03T06:43:32.812Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user typed \"/mew\" - this looks like it might be a slash command, but it's not one of the standard OpenClaw commands I know about. Let me check what this could mean.\n\nIt could be:\n1. A typo or random input\n2. A playful reference to \"mew\" (cat sound)\n3. Some kind of custom command they're trying\n4. A test to see how I respond\n\nGiven the playful \"hihi\" message earlier from the control UI, this seems like more playful interaction. I should respond in a friendly, slightly playful way but not assume it's a serious command unless they clarify.\n\nI'll keep it light and friendly, perhaps play along with the cat reference if that's what they're going for.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"😺 Mew?\n\nĐang thử nghiệm hả? Hay bạn thích mèo? \n\nCho tôi biết nếu bạn muốn tôi làm gì cụ thể nhé. Bây giờ tôi vẫn đang trong giai đoạn setup — tôi đã biết mình là trợ lý riêng của bạn, nhưng cần thêm thông tin để làm việc hiệu quả hơn."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":284,"output":380,"cacheRead":19566,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20230,"cost":{"input":0.0001704,"output":0.000836,"cacheRead":0.00215226,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0031586599999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775198595054,"responseId":"202604031443160ca88aaf41824cbe"}}
